How to run the app

1- From terminal
    write the programming language name,  then  the path of the file "main.dart"
    ex.      > dart  lib/main.dart


2-  from Top-Right                                (Run the same file , you are on it)
      from the Run Icon at the top-right

3-  from the left Icon
      but make sure to have the main.dart   in the "lib" folder ,      it save the path,  so u must make the main.dart in the "lib" folder


